snippet.title: Amber Heard EXPOSED Again! JOHNNY DEPP's Lawyer Questions Her Attorney ERIC GEORGE
snippet.description:
Full Deposition Read Through.  Amber Heard EXPOSED Again! JOHNNY DEPP's Lawyer Questions Her Attorney ERIC GEORGE. 
Ben Chew, an attorney for Johnny Depp questioned Amber Heard's former Lawyer Eric George in regards to the ACLU and the Op-ed written by them.

Johnny Depp has another win and things are looking good for the VA trial.
